yedere oygn zeen undz

216
00:14:03,441 --> 00:14:06,658
als merders far dem mir, m'iz yidn!

217
00:14:07,339 --> 00:14:10,657
nisht ayngenem. yedere trit,

218
00:14:15,608 --> 00:14:20,326
azoy iz es geven, m'hot gedankt az zey zenen shoyn nisht do.

219
00:14:21,312 --> 00:14:24,489
m'hot gedavnt, m'hot gezogt kadesh.

220
00:14:24,489 --> 00:14:25,625
in vald.

221
00:14:27,893 --> 00:14:33,354
un yetst hob ikh gevor gevorn vu mayn brud- vos iz sara fabrik!

222
00:14:33,512 --> 00:14:37,792
az der fabrik iz a lager,

223
00:14:38,524 --> 00:14:41,015
arbetn arbetn yidn,

224
00:14:41,663 --> 00:14:46,553
nor di fakhmanen zenen daytshn, vos zey kenen,

225
00:14:46,553 --> 00:14:51,629
un polyakn! vos zey kenen boyen FLUGZEUGes.

226
00:14:52,530 --> 00:14:57,587
mayn ma- mayn bruder ken zayn bar a mashin.

227
00:14:58,167 --> 00:15:05,197
aza m- mashin un m'vil nim, nim, er zol zayn

228
00:15:05,372 --> 00:15:07,273
un er hot zikh gemakht

229
00:15:07,633 --> 00:15:14,006
nisht- oyf di konte vos er hot, zayn kern-karte, hot men im gezogt, hot men im geshikt.

230
00:15:14,181 --> 00:15:18,911
in arbayts-amt, er zol zikh makhn a doike kern-karte,

231
00:15:18,911 --> 00:15:21,026
iz geganen un m'hot im gemakht.

232
00:15:22,838 --> 00:15:27,590
hot er, hot er shoyn a rikhtike kern-karte, un er arbet!

233
00:15:29,318 --> 00:15:30,763
nor vos?

234
00:15:30,853 --> 00:15:32,855
dortn arbetn yidn.

235
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:36,436
fun SANDOMIERZ,

236
00:15:36,436 --> 00:15:39,571
fun OPATÓW, fun KRAŚNIK,

237
00:15:39,578 --> 00:15:41,175
ale yidn,

238
00:15:42,852 --> 00:15:45,984
un zey arbetn tsuzamet, er lernt zey,

239
00:15:48,994 --> 00:15:56,953
mayn bruder n- nisht far dem er hot gevolt,

240
00:15:57,263 --> 00:16:02,100
nor er iz a guter mentsh algemeyn, nokh haynt,

241
00:16:02,342 --> 00:16:04,108
er voynt in Yisroel,

242
00:16:04,131 --> 00:16:05,984
yedern vet er helfn!

243
00:16:05,984 --> 00:16:09,997
un yidn, un dem, un di-o lager,

244
00:16:10,594 --> 00:16:12,970
er vet esn un zey veln nisht?

245
00:16:12,970 --> 00:16:18,722
hot er mir gezogt ikh zol brengen esn far dem er veyst nisht fun vanet zey tsu shafn,

246
00:16:19,538 --> 00:16:23,818
hob ikh nokh di arbet geganen un un gekoyft

247
00:16:23,892 --> 00:16:26,670
a bisl puter, a bisl,

248
00:16:26,794 --> 00:16:30,011
khazer, far dem andersh iz nisht gevezn,

249
00:16:30,608 --> 00:16:34,216
vos kh'hob gekent, un az kh'hob mikh getrofn mitn bruder

250
00:16:34,216 --> 00:16:36,323
bin ikh geganen mit a TECZKA,

251
00:16:36,683 --> 00:16:38,983
nisht keyn groyse, a TECZKA,

252
00:16:38,983 --> 00:16:41,809
geken- g- zol gebn, hob ikh,

253
00:16:41,809 --> 00:16:45,368
iz gevezn finef kilometer in vald arayn,

254
00:16:45,643 --> 00:16:50,007
in dortn hot men gehat mayn plats, un ikh hob mikh getrofn

255
00:16:50,115 --> 00:16:52,179
tsvey molt in di vokh,

256
00:16:52,179 --> 00:16:55,880
finef kilometer iz far mir geven a shprung!

257
00:16:56,443 --> 00:16:58,091
yung! a loyf!

258
00:16:58,468 --> 00:17:04,234
un kh'hob mikh getrofn dort mitn bruder, un er hot dos gegebn di yidn.

259
00:17:04,712 --> 00:17:10,809
nor di yidn hobn nisht getort zogn di polyakn, un zey hobn nisht getort zogn

260
00:17:10,809 --> 00:17:18,459
di daytshn, nisht far dem m'hot zey gezogt, zey hobn gehaltn mayn bruder alts heyliker,

261
00:17:18,567 --> 00:17:20,310
men muz nim hitn,

262
00:17:20,310 --> 00:17:26,711
far dem er vet blaybn nokh di krig, un er vet fartseyln vos s'iz gevezn.

263
00:17:31,729 --> 00:17:38,794
mayn, mayn bruder hobn zey geshikt er zol koyf- zey viln gever hobn.

264
00:17:40,015 --> 00:17:41,882
hobn zey nim gegebn

265
00:17:42,951 --> 00:17:49,006
er zol koyfn dortn in Varshe gever, er ken forn far dem, er hot nisht keyn opaske.

266
00:17:49,006 --> 00:17:51,503
vayl nokh di arbet, shabes,

267
00:17:51,503 --> 00:17:56,343
un zuntik, ken er forn, un zey hobn nim gegebn epes adresn

268
00:17:56,620 --> 00:17:59,434
az zi zol, er zol zikh vendn.

269
00:17:59,434 --> 00:18:01,490
er iz geforn nokh Varshe,

270
00:18:01,665 --> 00:18:04,426
nor keyn gever hot er nisht gekent koyfn.

271
00:18:04,652 --> 00:18:08,679
s'iz nim nisht gelungen. er hot nisht gevust vos un WANN.

272
00:18:10,879 --> 00:18:15,525
er hot getrofn dortn, farbundn zikh

273
00:18:15,525 --> 00:18:22,500
PAPIEROSazhes, di do vos in Varshe hobn farkoyft papirosn in gas, dos iz gevezn yidn.

274
00:18:22,945 --> 00:18:27,748
in er hot zikh opgeshtelt mit zey, efsher dos tsveyte mol.

275
00:18:27,771 --> 00:18:30,161
er hot nisht gekrign keyn gever.

276
00:18:31,230 --> 00:18:33,299
ober dortn hot er gearbet.

277
00:18:33,795 --> 00:18:37,924
un dortn iz gekumen mayn bruder oykhet.

278
00:18:38,284 --> 00:18:42,665
dents- ven her hot zikh, er hot nisht gelernt in di shule,

279
00:18:43,363 --> 00:18:48,448
iz er gekumen tsu forn. zikh trefn. un dos hob ikh gevust, ven mayn bruder vet zayn,

280
00:18:48,448 --> 00:18:50,613
un m'hot zikh getrofn in vald,

281
00:18:50,772 --> 00:18:52,892
un ikh hob gezogt, "s'iz shlekht."

282
00:18:53,438 --> 00:18:55,932
"m'hot nisht vos oyftsutun."

283
00:18:55,932 --> 00:19:05,193
"di daytshn kumen iberal, sh- shoyn Frankraykh, zey nemen ales ayn.

284
00:19:05,773 --> 00:19:08,366
ikh vil nisht mer," hob ikh gezogt.

285
00:19:09,385 --> 00:19:11,437
hot mayn bruder gezogt,

286
00:19:13,249 --> 00:19:20,617
"du vest zen, undz dray et men zikh nokh trefn nokh di krig, un di daytshe veln farshpiln!"

287
00:19:20,860 --> 00:19:25,039
ikh hob nisht gehaltn fun, mayn bruder zol zayn aza idyot!

288
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:27,080
er zol dos zogn!

289
00:19:27,795 --> 00:19:29,949
hob ikh shtark geveynt.

290
00:19:31,980 --> 00:19:35,180
er redt zakhene dume, dume zakhn.

291
00:19:36,942 --> 00:19:39,824
vos vet, vos vet nisht zayn.

292
00:19:39,824 --> 00:19:44,884
un do iz yedere tog iz geferlekh, geferlekh.

293
00:19:45,919 --> 00:19:48,683
me vet, az me shtimt zikh op

294
00:19:48,683 --> 00:19:53,287
veyst men keyn mol nisht oyb me vet zikh trefn, ober bald me vet undz nisht

295
00:19:54,255 --> 00:19:59,879
z-, az s'iz geven shney, hot men ge-, gemuzt geyn in shney in vald.

296
00:19:59,879 --> 00:20:01,860
un dos hot men gezen.

297
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:07,718
oyfn shosey, nu, undz hobn zey mikh nisht gekent azoy derkenen,

298
00:20:07,718 --> 00:20:11,414
nor di shney ken dokh oyszogn, di tritn,

299
00:20:11,414 --> 00:20:14,924
ver dortn ken geyn. s'iz dokh nisht fun keyn hunt, fun,

300
00:20:14,924 --> 00:20:16,575
nor s'iz fun mentshn.

301
00:20:17,121 --> 00:20:21,688
iz geven zeyer, zeyer ongeshtrengt.

302
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:25,029
ober tsvey molt in di vokh hob ikh mikh getrofn!

303
00:20:25,288 --> 00:20:27,543
far dem ikh bin geven shtark,

304
00:20:27,702 --> 00:20:29,940
kh'hob gevolt dos tun far mayn tatn.

305
00:20:32,140 --> 00:20:35,981
er iz gevezn vos er't gegloybt in di kinder.

306
00:20:36,291 --> 00:20:41,617
er't gegloybt in undzere zkhus az undz vet men nokh forn nokh Yisroel.

307
00:20:41,809 --> 00:20:43,254
nokh Palestine.

308
00:20:47,833 --> 00:20:50,746
dortn vu mayn bruder hot gearbet,

309
00:20:50,972 --> 00:20:53,176
hot gearbet polyakn oykhet.

310
00:20:53,959 --> 00:20:58,256
di polyakn hobn gezen az er tut epes mit di yidn.

311
00:21:00,186 --> 00:21:02,390
zey hobn gemasert di daytshn,

312
00:21:02,565 --> 00:21:05,512
az er iz epes mit di yidn,

313
00:21:08,387 --> 00:21:13,697
un der daytsh vos er hot gearbet mit mayn bruder,

314
00:21:13,753 --> 00:21:15,016
hot gezogt

315
00:21:15,016 --> 00:21:17,916
az, "der hot gezogt oyf dir

316
00:21:19,086 --> 00:21:24,075
andere daytshn, un zey zenen geganen tsum gestapo un m'vet kumen morgn nokh dir.

317
00:21:24,570 --> 00:21:25,644
in der fri."

318
00:21:27,287 --> 00:21:32,849
dentsmolt iz mayn bruder, yingere, gevezn bay im, bayn eltern,

319
00:21:33,852 --> 00:21:36,343
zey hobn gehat rovern tsu forn,

320
00:21:36,872 --> 00:21:38,655
er iz aheymgekumen,

321
00:21:38,678 --> 00:21:41,405
hobn zey bald genumen di rovern,

322
00:21:41,631 --> 00:21:44,612
un zey hobn ales ibergelozt un zey zenen antlofn.

323
00:21:46,643 --> 00:21:52,307
di yingere bruder iz geforn in di shule arayn,

324
00:21:54,220 --> 00:21:57,419
un der elterer iz geforn

325
00:21:58,607 --> 00:22:07,055
ikh veys nisht vu, geforn. mit banen zenen zey geforn, di rovern hobn zey ibergelozt, bay di ban, aroyfgezetst oyf di ban un geforn.

326
00:22:09,154 --> 00:22:14,430
er iz geforn nokh Kroke, der elterer, dernokh bin ikh gevor gevorn, un er hot gekrign an arbet.

327
00:22:16,495 --> 00:22:20,049
un er hot gekrign an arbet oykh in aza fabrik,

328
00:22:20,410 --> 00:22:23,098
nisht fun SAMOLOTn,

329
00:22:23,098 --> 00:22:28,959
nisht fun LUFTZEUGE, nor fun mashinen!

330
00:22:29,083 --> 00:22:30,747
ober bay mashinen.

331
00:22:32,273 --> 00:22:33,532
un UNK,

332
00:22:33,606 --> 00:22:35,540
kh'hob fargesn tsu zogn,

333
00:22:35,547 --> 00:22:37,897
az dortn vu er hot gearbet,

334
00:22:37,897 --> 00:22:43,184
di fabrik, un vu m'hot geboyt di LUFTZEUGE, hot geheysn BUDZYN,

335
00:22:43,191 --> 00:22:49,614
s'iz vikhtik tsu visn dem nomen, far dem s'iz do mentshn vos se lebn

336
00:22:49,857 --> 00:22:53,262
in Kalifornye, in Yisroel,

337
00:22:53,262 --> 00:22:55,228
vos zey kenen mayn bruder,

338
00:22:55,228 --> 00:22:57,528
vos hobn geshribn vegn dem,

339
00:22:59,357 --> 00:23:01,258
un vos hobn zikh geratevet.

340
00:23:02,057 --> 00:23:05,918
un vos hobn gezogt az ikh bin

341
00:23:05,918 --> 00:23:09,462
ŚWIĘTA MARIA, KEDOSHA, a heylike,

342
00:23:09,462 --> 00:23:12,817
far dem ikh bin mayn bruder's shveste- shvester.

343
00:23:13,212 --> 00:23:16,193
far dem vos me tut far zey. ze'mir heylike.

344
00:23:18,392 --> 00:23:25,037
BUDZYŃ. BUDZYŃ iz geven di fabrik in vos m'hot gearbet di SAMOLOTn.

345
00:23:18,416 --> 00:23:20,249
un un vos hot ir...

346
00:23:25,037 --> 00:23:26,654
di FLUGZEUGE.

347
00:23:26,965 --> 00:23:30,469
BUDZYŃ. un ikh hob gelebt in

348
00:23:30,947 --> 00:23:32,952
finef kilometer vayter

349
00:23:32,952 --> 00:23:35,331
in a sht- in a kleyn shtetl vos m'hot

350
00:23:35,331 --> 00:23:37,286
hot geheysn URZĘDÓW

351
00:23:39,030 --> 00:23:44,441
zol ikh fartseyln fun mir? ober fun, fun mir? in URZĘDÓW

352
00:23:42,590 --> 00:23:43,277
yo, fun...

353
00:23:46,725 --> 00:23:48,237
nokh frier,

354
00:23:48,413 --> 00:23:51,309
in URZĘDÓW iz shoyn nisht geven keyn yidn

355
00:23:53,205 --> 00:23:56,321
ikh hob gevoynt bay a poylishe,

356
00:23:56,428 --> 00:23:59,747
vos der man iz, hot gemakht

357
00:23:59,888 --> 00:24:02,717
di di kopetes far a ferd.

358
00:24:03,297 --> 00:24:05,282
dos hot geheysn koval,

359
00:24:06,756 --> 00:24:09,259
anshtendike mentshn, kh'hob geneyt,

360
00:24:09,259 --> 00:24:11,492
zi hot gehat tsvey tekhterlekh,

361
00:24:12,156 --> 00:24:14,225
un... azoy.

362
00:24:16,864 --> 00:24:19,299
un zi hot, zey hobn mikh tolerirt.

363
00:24:19,299 --> 00:24:20,773
iz geven gut.

364
00:24:22,365 --> 00:24:26,699
eyn molt, ikh bin geven azoy, zi iz geven BEFREUNDET mit mir,

365
00:24:26,699 --> 00:24:30,021
zogt zi, zi vil mikh argets nemen.

366
00:24:30,820 --> 00:24:32,518
ikh zol epes zen.

367
00:24:35,140 --> 00:24:40,601
zen, firt zi mikh bayn magistrat,

368
00:24:40,624 --> 00:24:44,465
iz do aza shtibl, un zi firt mikh dortn arayn,

369
00:24:44,539 --> 00:24:48,847
un dortn ze ikh tsvey

370
00:24:48,847 --> 00:24:52,902
tsvey, tate mit a mame mit tsvey kinder, yidishe!

371
00:24:55,778 --> 00:24:58,694
fartseyln zey, zi ken zey,

372
00:24:58,694 --> 00:25:00,592
zi iz geven BEFREUNDET mit ir,

373
00:25:00,592 --> 00:25:04,377
un zey hobn ir gegebn a tsetele aroys, zi zol zey kumen zen,

374
00:25:04,553 --> 00:25:05,976
un zi iz gekumen,

375
00:25:05,976 --> 00:25:08,698
fartseyln zey, oyf poylish,

376
00:25:09,261 --> 00:25:12,022
az zey hobn zikh nisht vu tsu bahaltn,

377
00:25:14,239 --> 00:25:17,340
⟨un⟩ zenen gekumen in magistrat arayn,

378
00:25:17,340 --> 00:25:22,062
zogn me zol epes tun mit zey, far dem zey hobn nisht vu tsu geyn,

379
00:25:29,123 --> 00:25:31,144
kh'ho- kh'hob nisht gevust

380
00:25:31,144 --> 00:25:35,124
ober ikh zol ariderfaln, ober vos, ober vos, ober vos,

381
00:25:37,560 --> 00:25:40,153
un do shteyt mayn, mayn

382
00:25:40,530 --> 00:25:42,161
mayn baleboste,

383
00:25:42,420 --> 00:25:43,640
zog ikh zi,

384
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:48,661
"far vos antloyft ets nisht in vald arayn?

385
00:25:48,661 --> 00:25:51,206
makhn dokh andere mentshn oykhet,"

386
00:25:51,448 --> 00:25:56,403
zogt zi, zogn zey, "in vald, s'iz do mosrim

387
00:25:57,203 --> 00:26:00,099
vos zey, zey kumen

388
00:26:01,101 --> 00:26:04,757
az se kumt emetser aroys fun vald, fun esn, hargenen zey."

389
00:26:05,117 --> 00:26:08,385
in zey hobn, un z-, zey hobn nisht vu tsu geyn,

390
00:26:08,931 --> 00:26:17,379
az m'iz gev-, nokh geven eyn mentsh, ken men nokh antloyfn, ober mit di kinder hot men nisht vos tsu makhn, m'hot nisht vu tsu geyn.

391
00:26:25,063 --> 00:26:29,043
iz nishto keyn verter, az men ken gornisht tun.

392
00:26:29,043 --> 00:26:30,863
dos harts kon platsn.

393
00:26:33,265 --> 00:26:38,371
m'hot nisht keyn plats tsu zayn oyf di arishe zayt,

394
00:26:39,154 --> 00:26:45,780
far dem der guf, iz, ober s'harts,

395
00:26:46,410 --> 00:26:51,365
iz dokh, iz dokh nisht zeyer, ken platsn.

396
00:26:51,574 --> 00:26:53,705
me ke- s'iz shver.

397
00:26:53,705 --> 00:26:57,254
un ikh bin nokh azoy shtark ineveynik,

398
00:26:57,531 --> 00:27:00,748
far vos?! far vos?!

399
00:27:01,294 --> 00:27:02,655
ikh ken nisht.

400
00:27:03,201 --> 00:27:05,017
ikh shlof nisht bay di nakht.

401
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:10,690
ober, fizish bin ikh nokh shtark,

402
00:27:10,690 --> 00:27:14,991
eyn molt ruft men zikh vider aroys mayne,

403
00:27:15,621 --> 00:27:18,959
ikh veys nisht, ikh bin geven azoy BEFREUNDET mit nir,

404
00:27:18,959 --> 00:27:22,078
farshteyt zi, az ikh broykh oykh tsu zen.

405
00:27:23,755 --> 00:27:26,077
zol ikh oyfshteyn un vayzn

406
00:27:26,387 --> 00:27:27,984
iz di gas,

407
00:27:29,256 --> 00:27:30,822
a kleyn shtetl,

408
00:27:30,822 --> 00:27:34,026
un me firt eynem fun hinter.

409
00:27:34,048 --> 00:27:37,907
me firt arayn in di shtot arayn, eynem,

410
00:27:41,980 --> 00:27:46,648
a hoykhn, sheynem yunger-man,

411
00:27:47,903 --> 00:27:56,891
vos er geyt a mener, a mener hemdl, nor s'iz azoy kurts,

412
00:27:57,083 --> 00:27:58,882
un er iz naket,

413
00:28:00,745 --> 00:28:02,606
un fun eyn zayt

414
00:28:02,606 --> 00:28:07,269
haltn im hintern ore- hintern orem

415
00:28:07,562 --> 00:28:09,904
a a a lomer, a lomer,

416
00:28:09,904 --> 00:28:11,001
firt nim,

417
00:28:11,001 --> 00:28:18,389
un er iz azoy hoykh un der lomer iz kleyn, un fun tsveyte zayt, hintern orem, firt im a sheygets.

418
00:28:18,514 --> 00:28:21,411
fun akht nayn yor alt.

419
00:28:21,619 --> 00:28:23,503
un zey firn im.

420
00:28:24,522 --> 00:28:27,638
ober aza sheynem yunger-man!

421
00:28:28,791 --> 00:28:34,506
mit zakhene shvartse glantsedike oygn,

422
00:28:34,714 --> 00:28:40,698
azoy sheyn vi Bar-Kokhbe, hob ikh gelernt!

423
00:28:41,008 --> 00:28:46,267
iz yidishe heldn hobn gekent zayn in di historye azoy sheyn.

424
00:28:47,083 --> 00:28:48,680
ober vos?

425
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:53,028
er hot sha- shvartse hor, geshoyrene sheyn,

426
00:28:53,028 --> 00:28:57,996
nor di hor shteyen, di hor zenen drotn,

